    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7743022">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7743022/" class="title-link">当年明月和吴思的结合体</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7743022"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4329002/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4329002-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4329002/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">宇文欢</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-20"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-20 16:51:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7743022_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  听说是天涯煮酒近年来的奇文，第一时间从卓越上买了。 一上来是袁世凯在朝鲜的那段往事，标签式的大段人物内心独白，让人很容易想到《明朝那些事儿》，不过我对那段历史的史料比较熟悉，马上就看出作者对于历史人物有自己的想法——袁世凯当然是有雄心的人，或者说野心，但是他...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7743022_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7743022_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7822186">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
